WEBVTT

00:01.734 --> 00:04.503
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:08.408 --> 00:11.043
 Lilith, do we have to do this? 

00:11.111 --> 00:14.546
Frasier, making out a will      
is a sensible precaution,       

00:14.614 --> 00:16.448
and one you've been             
avoiding for months.            

00:16.516 --> 00:18.350
We're seeing the lawyer         
this afternoon,                 

00:18.418 --> 00:20.486
and we have to get              
these questions answered.       

00:20.553 --> 00:22.021
                  Look, darling,

00:22.088 --> 00:24.857
         I find this entire will
        discussion troubling.   

00:24.924 --> 00:27.826
        It's not easy to talk   
          about one's mortality.

00:27.894 --> 00:29.628
                    Oh, just the
                thought of...   

00:29.696 --> 00:32.197
         of being apart from you
      and-and little Frederick--

00:32.265 --> 00:35.334
                it's... well,   
            it's-it's just hard.

00:35.402 --> 00:36.935
So, who gets the wok?           

00:37.003 --> 00:39.772
             The wok?!          

00:39.839 --> 00:42.374
            My God, woman, we're
    talking about death here!   

00:42.442 --> 00:43.642
        My death, your death,   

00:43.710 --> 00:45.044
          the end of everything!

00:45.111 --> 00:47.813
    Being lowered into the grave
         in a silk-lined casket!

00:47.881 --> 00:49.615
Yes. And?                       

00:49.683 --> 00:51.617
              And it's upsetting

00:51.685 --> 00:53.619
             to mammals like me!

00:55.121 --> 00:57.022
                Look, Lilith,   

00:57.090 --> 01:00.159
         all my life, I've had a
    problem talking about death.

01:00.226 --> 01:02.995
         I know it's irrational,
        but I can't help feeling

01:03.063 --> 01:05.164
                that if you talk
         about it, it'll happen.

01:05.230 --> 01:06.999
Well, Frasier,                  
it will happen.                 

01:07.067 --> 01:08.667
                        Stop it.

01:08.735 --> 01:10.302
What, do you think              

01:10.370 --> 01:13.238
if I hadn't mentioned it,       
you'd live forever?             

01:14.741 --> 01:16.642
                 Well, now we'll
            never know, will we?

01:18.878 --> 01:20.846
      (theme song begins)       

