    ¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶      

01:25.352 --> 01:28.454
¶ Takes everything you've got ¶ 

01:28.521 --> 01:31.123
        ¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶     

01:31.191 --> 01:34.593
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

01:34.661 --> 01:38.497
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

01:39.566 --> 01:42.034
  ¶ Sometimes you want to go ¶  

01:42.102 --> 01:46.538
    ¶ Where everybody           
    knows your name ¶           

01:47.841 --> 01:52.444
      ¶ And they're always      
        glad you came ¶         

